WEBVTT

00:18.309 --> 00:20.562
THAT DAY…

00:27.819 --> 00:31.239
WAS JUST ANOTHER ORDINARY DAY

00:36.870 --> 00:39.497
-Can I have it as a set menu?
-It's not available…

00:39.581 --> 00:42.459
We have your drinks ready, ma'am.

00:44.335 --> 00:45.754
-Thank you.
-Enjoy.

00:47.714 --> 00:50.216
Hey, wait for me.
Don't watch it without me.

00:51.718 --> 00:52.886
Thank you.

00:52.969 --> 00:53.928
Firstly…

00:54.679 --> 00:57.182
an angel appears and prophecizes.

00:58.266 --> 01:00.935
The angel says
the name of the recipient first.

01:02.145 --> 01:05.774
They are then told when they will die
and that they are bound for Hell.

01:06.983 --> 01:08.485
When the time comes,

01:09.235 --> 01:13.865
the executors come from Hell
to fulfill the prophecy.

01:16.284 --> 01:18.161
If you're watching this
for the first time,

01:18.244 --> 01:19.621
you may find it shocking.

01:19.704 --> 01:21.414
He looks completely normal.

01:21.998 --> 01:23.917
But why is he talking nonsense?

01:24.584 --> 01:27.253
Does anyone even believe this bullshit?

01:27.337 --> 01:30.256
Lots of people believe this.

01:30.340 --> 01:33.051
Loads of videos
on his YouTube channel back it up.

01:33.551 --> 01:37.680
Come on. Con men like him can only exploit
people because idiots like you exist.

01:38.515 --> 01:40.850
Don't take this seriously, all right?

01:42.560 --> 01:45.522
Hey, don't tell me
you're already indoctrinated.

01:45.605 --> 01:46.523
What?

01:46.606 --> 01:48.733
Let's watch it again, then.

01:48.817 --> 01:50.193
This is all CGI.

01:50.276 --> 01:51.694
It's not.

01:56.866 --> 01:59.160
NOVEMBER 10, THURSDAY

02:13.800 --> 02:16.761
NOVEMBER 10, THURSDAY

02:38.283 --> 02:39.159
What's that?

02:41.995 --> 02:43.037
What's going on?

03:15.945 --> 03:17.155
Move!

03:18.364 --> 03:21.075
Damn it! Move out of my way!

03:21.159 --> 03:22.076
What the--

06:35.061 --> 06:36.562
-Hello, sir.
-Hi.

06:45.321 --> 06:48.199
-You punk!
-Stop, you bastard!

06:48.282 --> 06:49.867
-What the hell?
-Don't move!

06:49.951 --> 06:50.785
Damn.

06:50.868 --> 06:53.996
-You startled me. Take him away.
-It wasn't me! I didn't do it!

06:54.080 --> 06:55.289
Don't be too harsh.

06:56.499 --> 06:58.543
Damn, that startled me.

07:00.837 --> 07:04.090
We will now begin the case briefing

07:04.173 --> 07:07.343
on the Hapseong Station murder case.

07:08.219 --> 07:10.430
It occurred on November 10th, 2022.

07:10.513 --> 07:13.141
at a coffee shop near Hapseong Station.

07:13.224 --> 07:17.603
Some strange creatures appeared
out of nowhere and murdered the victim…

07:18.813 --> 07:20.064
The body ran…

07:20.148 --> 07:21.816
I mean, they burnt the body and ran.

07:22.400 --> 07:24.735
We are currently working on
tracking down the suspects.

07:25.736 --> 07:28.865
We have yet to find any evidence
at the scene.

07:30.283 --> 07:33.244
We still need to wait
for the full autopsy report,

07:33.744 --> 07:36.372
but it is clear that the body
was burnt to a crisp

07:36.456 --> 07:37.999
at a very high temperature.

07:38.082 --> 07:39.459
When did it start?

07:39.542 --> 07:43.379
-Just now.
-Here are the preliminary autopsy results.

07:44.839 --> 07:46.966
We do not have the full results yet,

07:48.050 --> 07:52.305
but the body seems to have been burnt at
a very high temperature in a short time.

07:52.388 --> 07:54.515
TRENDING: HELL, GOD, DEATH,
THE NEW TRUTH, ANGEL

07:54.599 --> 07:56.851
It's blowing up the Internet.

07:56.934 --> 07:59.645
The chief must be anxious as hell.

08:00.605 --> 08:01.814
…were able to identify him.

08:02.815 --> 08:04.692
Joo Myeonghun, age 36.

08:04.775 --> 08:08.237
He lived alone in an apartment
15 minutes away from the coffee shop.

08:08.321 --> 08:11.616
He divorced two years ago
and his ex-wife was his only family.

08:11.699 --> 08:14.035
He had no kids.

08:14.118 --> 08:16.078
It happened in broad daylight,

08:16.162 --> 08:19.081
so we've got tons of witnesses
and video evidence.

08:19.665 --> 08:20.875
Here's one of the clips.

08:24.795 --> 08:26.214
What is that?

08:28.716 --> 08:33.721
We can clearly see a strange creature
murdering the victim in this clip…

08:33.804 --> 08:34.639
What is that?

08:34.722 --> 08:37.934
…but we couldn't find
any physical evidence at the scene.

08:40.853 --> 08:43.523
"Jung Jinsu." "The New Truth"?
What are these?

08:43.606 --> 08:45.983
Kyunghun! Stop looking at your phone!

08:46.067 --> 08:47.401
He's going to cover it all!

08:47.902 --> 08:49.278
The New Truth.

08:49.362 --> 08:53.241
It was formed in 2012,
and it's recently become--

08:53.324 --> 08:54.283
That's enough.

08:56.536 --> 08:58.663
Everyone, listen.

08:58.746 --> 09:02.917
The media, the press, and the Internet…
They are all going wild over this case.

09:03.000 --> 09:04.919
You all need to do your job properly!

09:05.419 --> 09:08.422
Kids are already spreading
strange rumors about this case.

09:08.506 --> 09:10.883
But is it even human?

09:10.967 --> 09:11.884
Just bring it in!

09:11.968 --> 09:14.887
We'll find out what it is
once we have it in custody.

09:14.971 --> 09:17.640
Unit One, do some legwork
and find more about the victim.

09:17.723 --> 09:19.809
-Yes, sir.
-Unit Two, go check the scene.

09:19.892 --> 09:22.103
Question those who were
at the coffee shop.

09:22.186 --> 09:25.690
Make sure you don't give reporters
any info. They'll only spread rumors.

09:25.773 --> 09:28.317
-And Kyunghun.
-Yes, sir.

09:28.401 --> 09:31.737
Team up with Eunpyo
and find more about the New Truth.

09:31.821 --> 09:33.864
They are having a gathering
near the scene.

09:33.948 --> 09:37.118
It looks like those fanatics
are related to this case somehow.

09:37.201 --> 09:39.453
-You two, go check on them.
-Yes, sir.

09:39.537 --> 09:41.330
-Do not incite them.
-Okay.

09:41.414 --> 09:43.583
It's best not to mess
with religious groups.

09:43.666 --> 09:45.543
-Everyone, get to work!
-Yes, sir.

09:48.713 --> 09:49.714
Kyunghun.

09:50.298 --> 09:51.549
-Yes, sir.
-Come here.

09:57.555 --> 10:01.017
Feel free to let me know if you need
some time away from the field.

10:03.769 --> 10:05.771
I'm a detective. What else would I do?

10:05.855 --> 10:06.689
That's not…

10:08.357 --> 10:10.359
At least be on time, then.

10:27.293 --> 10:28.711
"The New Truth."

10:29.587 --> 10:33.090
"An organization for religious studies
formed by Chairman Jung Jinsu in 2012."

10:34.050 --> 10:36.177
The group hasn't been around long.

10:36.677 --> 10:38.554
Just a little over ten years.

10:39.430 --> 10:40.598
What are you reading?

10:41.265 --> 10:43.601
Oh, this? It's an online encyclopedia.

10:43.684 --> 10:44.810
You punk.

10:44.894 --> 10:48.481
"They have never disclosed
the exact number of members,

10:48.564 --> 10:52.401
but it is assumed that its radical members
formed the Arrowhead."

10:52.485 --> 10:54.278
What? The Arrowhead?

10:54.945 --> 10:57.698
You mean those psychos
who leak ex-cons' identities online?

10:57.782 --> 10:59.200
Are they part of the New Truth?

10:59.283 --> 11:03.829
From what I know,
the Arrowhead isn't just active online.

11:04.747 --> 11:07.416
I've heard of them
being involved in petty crimes.

11:08.084 --> 11:09.210
It says here

11:09.877 --> 11:14.757
that an angel-like figure appears
and tells you when you will go to Hell.

11:17.093 --> 11:21.597
"Hell" and "angel"? Are they saying
this is divine retribution?

11:21.681 --> 11:25.059
Yes. "An angel prophecizes
an individual's time of death,

11:25.142 --> 11:28.145
and when that time comes,
executors come up from Hell,

11:28.229 --> 11:31.190
demonstrate the pain of Hell
and disappear."

11:31.273 --> 11:34.610
They say it's some kind
of warning to the people.

11:34.694 --> 11:38.072
So are they saying
what we saw earlier is God's work?

11:38.155 --> 11:39.657
Their doctrine is full of holes,

11:39.740 --> 11:42.493
but people are attracted
by the video evidence they present.

11:43.244 --> 11:45.621
Kids learn everything
from videos these days.

11:47.748 --> 11:50.167
Whether it's God's work or not,
I hope it's true.

11:50.251 --> 11:52.086
Why do you say that?

11:52.169 --> 11:53.337
Think about it.

11:54.255 --> 11:57.925
Whenever we bring in all those
evil bastards who deserve death,

11:58.008 --> 12:01.429
the court lets them off
based on something trivial.

12:06.058 --> 12:06.934
Sorry.

12:07.768 --> 12:09.103
Our job is to catch them.

12:09.854 --> 12:11.814
Whether their victim is good or bad,

12:12.565 --> 12:15.109
whether they killed
to save the world or for fun…

12:15.693 --> 12:18.946
No matter what their reason is,
we're supposed to catch murderers.

12:19.029 --> 12:20.698
That's all we need to think about.

12:23.743 --> 12:27.037
Send backup to sector two and three.

12:32.084 --> 12:32.960
Open the gate.

12:45.473 --> 12:48.601
Patrol team moving to sector four.

12:55.274 --> 12:59.195
Code two-one moving to sector three.

13:02.865 --> 13:05.326
Patrol team report position. Patrol team…

13:05.409 --> 13:07.953
I didn't expect to see you at the scene.

13:08.037 --> 13:09.747
-Hey, Kyunghun.
-Hello.

13:10.581 --> 13:13.042
The damn team leader is on vacation.

13:14.001 --> 13:16.837
And since all eyes are on this case,

13:16.921 --> 13:18.714
I had to be here.

13:21.175 --> 13:22.593
Did you find anything?

13:22.676 --> 13:24.011
Nothing.

13:24.094 --> 13:27.723
The witness testified
that the creature excreted bodily fluids,

13:27.807 --> 13:29.266
but there's no trace.

13:29.350 --> 13:31.185
There aren't any footprints either.

13:31.268 --> 13:33.145
All we got were bloodstains.

13:33.938 --> 13:34.939
Look over there.

13:35.815 --> 13:37.691
They all belong to the victim.

13:38.400 --> 13:39.360
Oh dear.

13:41.278 --> 13:44.031
I heard the New Truth
is having a gathering here.

13:44.114 --> 13:44.990
Over there.

13:45.741 --> 13:47.743
Maybe that's them.

13:48.327 --> 13:51.247
They've been blabbering
into a microphone for a while.

13:51.330 --> 13:52.915
-See you, then.
-All right.

13:52.998 --> 13:53.958
See you later, sir.

13:54.834 --> 13:58.629
That sin signifies God's message.

13:58.712 --> 14:01.507
We need to listen
to God's voice, starting now.

14:03.676 --> 14:06.554
This person, who lived
in a village in South East Asia,

14:07.137 --> 14:09.932
had received a prophecy from an angel

14:10.432 --> 14:12.810
that he would go to Hell in five hours.

14:12.893 --> 14:13.727
Then…

14:13.811 --> 14:15.312
WHAT IS "GOD'S WILL"?

14:23.362 --> 14:26.198
This was filmed exactly five hours
after he received the prophecy.

14:33.289 --> 14:36.292
A few days later,

14:36.375 --> 14:39.336
three bodies were found buried
at the man's house.

14:40.963 --> 14:43.924
They were missing persons
from unsolved cases.

14:47.636 --> 14:49.388
This was taken seven years ago in Japan.

14:51.015 --> 14:54.018
This person had multiple counts
of fraud and assault.

14:55.603 --> 14:59.064
This was from Nicaragua six years ago.
Child exploitation and murder.

14:59.648 --> 15:01.942
At a glance, they look similar,

15:02.026 --> 15:04.904
and were all killed in the same way,
as you saw in the video.

15:05.696 --> 15:07.656
And they were all criminals.

15:09.992 --> 15:11.201
Manufacturing narcotics.

15:12.536 --> 15:13.454
Robbery and theft.

15:14.413 --> 15:15.289
Fraud.

15:15.372 --> 15:17.291
Rape, arson…

15:19.919 --> 15:21.503
Why do people sin?

15:22.922 --> 15:25.007
People who say they value humanity,

15:25.633 --> 15:27.843
above everything else,

15:28.510 --> 15:29.970
make excuses like this.

15:31.889 --> 15:33.557
Because they had a tough childhood,

15:34.058 --> 15:36.310
because of structural inequality,

15:36.393 --> 15:38.354
because they have a mental disorder,

15:38.854 --> 15:41.690
because they were under the influence
of drugs and alcohol.

15:44.068 --> 15:45.319
The concept of sin exists

15:46.487 --> 15:49.490
because humans choose to sin.

15:50.157 --> 15:52.159
As a result of denying that fact,

15:52.242 --> 15:54.745
we humans have forgotten
about shame, remorse,

15:54.828 --> 15:57.623
repentance, and redemption.

15:58.958 --> 16:02.753
God has found a way
to directly present to you

16:03.754 --> 16:06.966
what Hell is like.

16:08.467 --> 16:10.344
Why would God do this?

16:13.764 --> 16:17.518
He's telling us to be more righteous.

16:24.566 --> 16:26.568
Chairman Jung, you did great today.

16:26.652 --> 16:28.862
-Thank you. Safe trip back home.
-Thank you.

16:29.363 --> 16:30.614
Chairman Jung Jinsu?

16:33.659 --> 16:37.246
-Oh, I guess you are newcomers.
-We're from the police.

16:39.999 --> 16:41.000
Hello.

16:41.625 --> 16:43.043
Hello.

16:44.753 --> 16:46.338
What brings you here, Detectives?

16:46.422 --> 16:49.216
We're investigating the murder
that occurred over there today.

16:49.800 --> 16:51.760
-Murder case?
-Yes.

16:55.472 --> 16:57.808
I guess you're talking about
the demonstration.

17:01.270 --> 17:04.982
It's funny how you investigate
God's deeds.

17:06.483 --> 17:07.484
I understand.

17:08.110 --> 17:10.863
In your eyes, it's still a murder.

17:10.946 --> 17:13.657
Heejung, I got this. Give it to me.

17:13.741 --> 17:15.409
-Take a break.
-Thank you.

17:15.492 --> 17:18.120
Someone has died so we must investigate.

17:18.203 --> 17:19.455
So how may I help you?

17:20.247 --> 17:21.248
Well…

17:22.291 --> 17:23.917
-Heejung! Hey!
-Kyunghun.

17:24.001 --> 17:25.961
What are you doing here?

17:26.462 --> 17:28.756
Let go, Dad! Let go of me!

17:29.256 --> 17:32.342
Aren't you supposed to be at the academy?
What are you doing here?

17:32.426 --> 17:33.385
Hi, Heejung.

17:34.094 --> 17:35.387
It's been a while.

17:35.971 --> 17:37.264
You're so tall now.

17:37.347 --> 17:38.515
Hello.

17:39.558 --> 17:41.560
I'm on my way there now. Don't worry.

17:41.643 --> 17:43.812
Go straight home after class, all right?

17:43.896 --> 17:45.230
Okay, I got it.

17:46.940 --> 17:48.859
Chairman Jung, I'll get going.

17:49.568 --> 17:51.487
Okay. Bye, Heejung.

17:52.905 --> 17:54.239
Thank you for today.

17:54.323 --> 17:55.866
What do you think you're doing?

17:58.327 --> 18:00.996
Heejung once told me
that her father is in the police.

18:01.830 --> 18:03.290
What a coincidence.

18:03.373 --> 18:05.834
Does your organization
take advantage of minors?

18:05.918 --> 18:06.960
Of course not.

18:07.795 --> 18:09.880
I got to know her through volunteer work.

18:11.256 --> 18:13.342
Since you don't find it appropriate,

18:13.425 --> 18:16.470
I'll tell her to refrain
from volunteering from now on.

18:18.138 --> 18:20.140
Well, anyway,

18:20.224 --> 18:23.310
we'd like to ask you
a few questions regarding the case.

18:24.061 --> 18:26.188
I'm sorry,
but I have an interview scheduled.

18:26.271 --> 18:29.149
-Do you mind if I answer them on the way?
-Not at all.

18:29.233 --> 18:30.234
Shall we?

18:31.610 --> 18:33.153
Let's follow him for now.

18:39.743 --> 18:43.580
Thank you for waiting.
The train will be departing shortly.

18:45.332 --> 18:47.626
Is this how you usually commute,
Chairman Jung?

18:47.709 --> 18:49.837
You do not need to address me as Chairman.

18:49.920 --> 18:53.132
You can just call me by my name.

18:53.715 --> 18:56.885
The members helped me get a car,

18:56.969 --> 19:00.139
but I prefer to use public transit.

19:01.890 --> 19:02.933
I guess

19:04.226 --> 19:07.980
you expected me to be
some kind of cult leader.

19:09.356 --> 19:10.816
I'm not like that at all.

19:12.359 --> 19:15.070
I'm sure you have a lot of questions.

19:16.405 --> 19:20.784
How can humans ever
fully understand God's work?

19:21.493 --> 19:23.787
Have you always been a believer?

19:24.413 --> 19:25.914
Not really.

19:25.998 --> 19:29.168
I grew up in a Catholic orphanage.

19:29.251 --> 19:31.253
Religion's always been part of my life.

19:36.466 --> 19:37.384
Chairman Jung!

19:38.051 --> 19:39.094
Please take my seat.

19:39.761 --> 19:41.555
No, it's okay. There's no need.

19:41.638 --> 19:44.266
Please, you should take this seat.

19:44.349 --> 19:45.350
No, thank you.

19:46.143 --> 19:47.936
Hey, that's Jung Jinsu.

19:48.020 --> 19:52.149
-Where? You're right, it is him.
-He's so cool.

19:55.402 --> 19:57.112
As I matured with age,

19:58.363 --> 20:00.240
I had always wanted to die.

20:01.116 --> 20:02.326
To tell you the truth,

20:03.619 --> 20:05.537
I had no interest in life.

20:08.207 --> 20:11.376
I was looking forward to turning 20,
wondering how to end my life.

20:11.877 --> 20:13.587
Why 20, specifically?

20:14.296 --> 20:17.174
Once you turn 20,
you get to leave the orphanage

20:17.257 --> 20:19.009
with some financial support.

20:21.220 --> 20:22.804
I was determined to end my life,

20:23.764 --> 20:26.975
but I didn't want people to see me dead.

20:29.561 --> 20:31.688
So I traveled to a plain in Tibet.

20:45.535 --> 20:49.873
There, vultures take care of dead bodies.

21:38.380 --> 21:42.884
That was the first time
I found meaning in life.

21:46.805 --> 21:50.183
Ever since, I traveled all over,
looking for traces of God.

21:50.684 --> 21:52.352
After traveling for ten years,

21:52.936 --> 21:55.355
I got to understand
God's will a little.

22:02.863 --> 22:06.616
And I realized what I was meant to do.

22:07.117 --> 22:09.619
Some people are saying that the New Truth

22:10.829 --> 22:13.415
is closely associated with the Arrowhead.

22:15.167 --> 22:17.878
I feel regretful about that claim.

22:19.546 --> 22:21.715
There are some people

22:21.798 --> 22:25.635
who misinterpret our doctrine
and have radical ideas.

22:27.054 --> 22:30.807
Letting the world know of God's wish
for us to live more righteously.

22:31.600 --> 22:33.685
That's our only goal.

22:39.232 --> 22:40.776
What's so funny?

22:41.318 --> 22:43.945
Living by performing good deeds
in fear of damnation…

22:45.614 --> 22:47.282
Can we call that just?

22:47.866 --> 22:50.577
Aside from fear,
what else makes people repent?

22:51.536 --> 22:53.455
Are you aware of anything else?

22:53.955 --> 22:55.749
According to you,

22:57.501 --> 23:00.796
this God must not believe
in humankind's free will.

23:03.131 --> 23:05.884
That's an interesting point,
Detective Jin.

23:07.886 --> 23:09.471
Free will…

23:09.554 --> 23:10.389
Right.

23:14.476 --> 23:15.769
I heard from Heejung

23:17.813 --> 23:21.400
that your wife was murdered.

23:24.319 --> 23:27.197
I can't begin to imagine
the pain you went through.

23:28.740 --> 23:31.118
What is the murderer doing now?

23:34.121 --> 23:37.874
Hasn't he been released back into society?

23:39.835 --> 23:44.631
Do you think that man-made laws
help justice be served?

23:47.717 --> 23:50.512
Do you think the murderer
feels any remorse?

23:51.763 --> 23:53.056
Chairman Jung?

23:55.142 --> 23:57.644
Hi, I'm here for your interview.

23:57.727 --> 23:58.603
Hello.

24:05.444 --> 24:06.486
That's my number.

24:07.154 --> 24:10.198
Please feel free to contact me
if you have any additional questions.

24:10.282 --> 24:11.366
Bye, then.

24:16.121 --> 24:17.622
-This way, please.
-Okay.

24:19.040 --> 24:20.417
Does he really live in there?

24:21.460 --> 24:23.086
He really is something.

24:26.715 --> 24:30.677
Did you expect a cult leader
to be ordinary?

25:05.462 --> 25:06.421
Heejung.

25:30.111 --> 25:32.489
Don't wash it.
I'm going to wear it tomorrow.

25:37.619 --> 25:38.912
We need to talk.

25:40.497 --> 25:42.332
I'm not a fanatic or anything.

25:42.415 --> 25:44.668
I attended a few of his lectures
out of curiosity.

25:44.751 --> 25:46.044
Don't worry.

25:46.711 --> 25:48.463
I haven't missed any school.

25:51.925 --> 25:52.926
Are we done?

26:10.151 --> 26:13.196
CHAIRMAN JUNG OF THE NEW TRUTH
RECEIVES CITIZEN AWARD FOR BRAVERY

