35:13.194 --> 35:15.655
I'm sorry.

35:16.697 --> 35:21.869
I denied God… I mean, I denied God's will.

35:21.953 --> 35:25.289
-I thought of pursuing worldly values.
-Boring.

35:25.373 --> 35:27.625
-I valued them above all--
-I can't hear you.

35:29.627 --> 35:31.337
Come to your senses!

35:31.420 --> 35:33.631
Look at him trying to look cool.

35:33.714 --> 35:34.841
Beat him!

35:36.717 --> 35:38.261
I'm gonna beat him up.

35:39.178 --> 35:41.806
METHOD_44: THAT LOOKS LIKE KIM GWANGJIN
ARROWFIRE: ARROWHEAD SWAG

35:42.306 --> 35:44.058
Who cares about your opinion?

35:44.142 --> 35:48.062
