and ask for God's forgiveness!

35:48.146 --> 35:50.356
-That's right.
-I'm so sorry.

35:51.023 --> 35:53.943
-I just wanted to sound smart.
-We can't hear you.

35:54.026 --> 35:55.069
I'm so sorry.

35:55.153 --> 35:58.739
I should've known my place
and kept my mouth shut.

35:59.407 --> 36:01.159
Please don't kill me.

36:02.743 --> 36:05.079
I'm so sorry.

36:06.956 --> 36:08.207
Great job!

36:08.791 --> 36:11.169
Well, he didn't even thank us

36:11.252 --> 36:13.296
for putting him back on the right path,

36:13.379 --> 36:16.007
