if you find anything, all right?

37:19.612 --> 37:20.696
Call me!

37:21.280 --> 37:22.323
Joo Myeonghun?

37:23.407 --> 37:24.492
Listen.

37:25.284 --> 37:27.787
How can we investigate
when there's nothing to convict?

37:27.870 --> 37:32.208
I get what you mean,
but that's not how filing a claim works.

37:32.708 --> 37:35.294
What do you mean
we should investigate the victim?

37:35.378 --> 37:38.673
If there's anything we should investigate,

37:38.756 --> 37:40.967
