but they're refusing to testify.

37:55.106 --> 37:56.524
Was that a live broadcast?

37:56.607 --> 37:58.985
Those reckless little punks.

37:59.068 --> 38:01.737
I don't know if those teenagers
are fearless or stupid.

38:02.238 --> 38:04.865
What about the novelist? How is he?

38:04.949 --> 38:08.035
