with his lawyer for the statement.

38:08.119 --> 38:09.954
I guess he doesn't need hospitalization.

38:14.667 --> 38:17.628
All right. Talk to those kids with Wonpil.

38:17.712 --> 38:19.463
I'll talk to the victim.

38:19.547 --> 38:22.049
We should've brought in
the skull mask guy.

38:22.133 --> 38:23.968
-I'll see you later.
-All right.

38:27.096 --> 38:27.930
Hello.

38:29.515 --> 38:31.517
I'm Assistant Inspector Jin Kyunghun.

38:31.600 --> 38:33.936
