38:52.913 --> 38:53.998
These little shits…

38:54.081 --> 38:56.125
-Wonpil, they're just kids.
-So damn cool.

38:56.208 --> 38:59.962
Behave and don't get on our nerves.

39:00.046 --> 39:03.883
Are they playing
good cop, bad cop with us?

39:03.966 --> 39:05.676
Shut up, you shithead.

39:05.760 --> 39:07.803
-Don't fucking talk to me.
-Why so serious?

39:07.887 --> 39:08.971
Seriously.

39:09.555 --> 39:11.015
I had a lecture,

39:11.724 --> 39:15.061
so I was on my way
to the underground parking lot.

39:16.145 --> 39:17.813
