of all those who were involved.

40:06.195 --> 40:07.738
Hello, juvenile court!

40:08.948 --> 40:10.157
Hey,

40:10.241 --> 40:12.701
Mr. Po-po is being serious. Look at him.

40:13.285 --> 40:14.120
Mister,

40:14.703 --> 40:18.541
