43:46.498 --> 43:47.333
Pardon?

43:49.501 --> 43:50.919
I'm bound for Hell.

43:51.503 --> 43:52.379
Hell?

43:52.463 --> 43:53.714
-Show her.
-Okay.

43:55.215 --> 43:56.050
