44:04.308 --> 44:07.061
Park Jungja.

44:07.728 --> 44:11.106
-You will die five days from now.
-What is this?

44:11.190 --> 44:14.443
-At 3:00 p.m.
-It's a decree.

44:15.569 --> 44:17.946
